<div class="disc">
  <strong>Medical Disclaimer</strong><br>
  This article is for educational and informational purposes only. It is not medical advice and does not recommend the use of any peptide. Dosing information is provided for reference only. Always consult a qualified healthcare provider before starting any peptide protocol. Individual responses vary, and quality control in unregulated markets poses real risks.
</div>

